snippet.title: Lewis Carroll's Alice | Gameplay: Chapter 1-The White Rabbit
snippet.description:
Xbox:
https://www.xbox.com/games/store/lewis-carrolls-alice/9p4wjkz3whd3
Steam:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2079530/Lewis_Carrolls_Alice/

Developed and published by Revie Studios.  

Based on Lewis Carroll's beloved 1865 children's book, Alice's Adventures in Wonderland, and featuring Sir John Tenniel's original illustrations.  A young girl named Alice falls through a rabbit hole into a fantasy world of anthropomorphic creatures.

Experience an interactive retelling of the classic tale by taking control of Alice in key moments, such as when Alice follows the White Rabbit down the rabbit hole. Relive the original unedited story and enjoy activities across a wide assortment of fun and relaxing mini-games, including croquet, swimming in the pool of tears, playing catch with a giant puppy, painting white roses red, and more.
